      "span_text": "The synthesis of G4.5-PEG followed our previous work.  Upon removal of methanol from G4.5 PAMAM stock solution by rotary evaporation, G4.5 PAMAM dendrimer (5 mg) was dissolved in 2 mL of sodium PBS (0.1 M, pH = 5.5).",
